data.description: Escape to your own secluded retreat in Dahlonega's tranquil countryside, just minutes away from 400. This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom ranch home sits on a sprawling 1.33-acre wooded lot, offering privacy and serenity. Step into the inviting oak eat-in kitchen, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining guests. The living room boasts a dining area, while a separate den features a cozy brick fireplace, ideal for relaxing evenings. The full unfinished basement includes boat doors and is stubbed for a bath, providing endless possibilities for customization and expansion. Additional features include a central vacuum and hookup for an emergency generator, ensuring convenience and peace of mind. Outside, a screened porch and deck overlook the lush and private fenced backyard, creating the perfect setting for outdoor enjoyment and relaxation. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to embrace the beauty of country living with easy access to modern conveniences! Home features new roof and water heater replaced in 2023, well pump tank, and the furnace replaced in 2022. Schedule your appt today!
